title: [1508521049] Spiced Grilled Chicken Wraps - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Marinate chicken in herbs and spices and cook on a hot griddle pan. Fill tortilla wraps with chicken, salad and chilli sauce for a healthy and delicious dinner.
